{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"布林","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Boolean","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>在電腦科學中，<strong>布林值</strong>是一種其值僅能為<em>真</em>或<em>假</em>的邏輯資料型別，它是編程語言裡在邏輯上表達真或假的方式。如果沒有這種能力，很多功能會無法實現。舉個例子，JavaScript 中的 <em>if 語句</em>的判斷條件會利用布林值來決定接下來的代碼是否要被執行。又如 JavaScript 中的 <em>for 循環</em>，如果沒有一個能夠解釋成不林值的判斷條件，循環將不知道是否要繼續循環或停止。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/*JavaScript if Statement*/</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>boolean conditional<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//coding</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"boolean conditional resolved to true\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"boolean conditional resolved to false\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/*JavaScript for Loop*/</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>control variable<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> boolean conditional<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> counter<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">//coding</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"I print only when the boolean conditional is true\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常規知識","title":"常規知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boolean_data_type\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Boolean</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術參考","title":"技術參考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>The JavaScript global object: <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/Data_structures\">JavaScript data types and data structures</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"在電腦科學中，布林值是一種其值僅能為真或假的邏輯資料型別，它是編程語言裡在邏輯上表達真或假的方式。如果沒有這種能力，很多功能會無法實現。舉個例子，JavaScript 中的 if 語句的判斷條件會利用布林值來決定接下來的代碼是否要被執行。又如 JavaScript 中的 for 循環，如果沒有一個能夠解釋成不林值的判斷條件，循環將不知道是否要繼續循環或停止。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Boolean","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Boolean","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Booléen","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Boolean","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"불린","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Booleano","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Boolean (Булев, Логический тип данных)","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Boolean","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/boolean","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/boolean/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Boolean","title":"布林"}],"pageTitle":"布林 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}